{"id": 1989, "genre": 1000, "title": "你无法忍受哪些被 App 强行煽情的时刻？", "description": "让人有点犯尴尬症的“温暖”、“关爱”，还是……算了吧。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 14305, "comment_count": 30, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171102115550ZiLNfloyzrY08Tv3.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-02T17:00:16Z", "questions": [{"id": 3219, "title": "你无法忍受哪些被 App 强行煽情的时刻？", "content": "你无法忍受哪些被 App 强行煽情的时刻？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 245813, "content": "动不动就提醒“若干年前的今天，你在……”", "image": "img/option/option/20171102160655PjWAbiY1lkfFVNHv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 245815, "content": "定期弹出提醒“以下朋友你已经很久没有联系了，要不要问候一下”", "image": "img/option/option/20171102155819Tsj1g4ZUEfLql2mz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 245816, "content": "提示“今天是你注册的第 1000 天，感谢我们一起走过的时光”，给自己加戏", "image": "img/option/option/20171102150045ownu7aspO8DxPgHi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 245818, "content": "所有添加的好友都有生日提醒，隔三岔五让我送电子贺卡", "image": "img/option/option/201711021448127DapJqKy0rcTN3mn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 245819, "content": "学习、运动软件推送或界面中时不时有不合时宜的“名人格言”激励你使用", "image": "img/option/option/20171102145206z6JTC5EdfcNHGs9p.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 245824, "content": "套用“日签”“一日签”体说话，无论和 App 功能是否有关", "image": "img/option/option/20171102155732V4H9NWxIo7Ucfaqs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 245825, "content": "几天没打开就“你有15天没来看我了，我为小主准备了七折优惠券，要来哦”", "image": "img/option/option/2017110215120154grNAol0PQTCusJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 245892, "content": "推送选择套近乎的时机和语言，类似于“深夜了，还不休息吗”", "image": "img/option/option/201711021618328S9y1CoJxBtlbOvr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}